Open Source report that visualise all test results, displaying 

1. Installing Mocha

Open Terminal, and type the following:
    sudo npm install -g mocha

2. Installing mochawesome reporting

    npm install -g mochawesome

    call: mocha test --reporter mochawesome --reporter-options charts=true --reporter-options autoOpen=true


OBSERVATIONS:
Mocha is super similar to testNG



